Before release:

1. Check milestone is complete

    https://github.com/AshleyYakeley/Truth/milestones

2. Pull upstream changes

    git checkout master
    git pull

3. Update version numbers

    Makefile
    */package.yaml
    support/vsc-extension/package.json
    support/pygments-lexer/setup.py
    pinafore/app/Version.hs
    mkdocs/docs/index.md

4. Update changelog

    deb/changelog.m4

5. Use latest LTS resolver

    https://www.stackage.org/lts
    stack.yaml
    docker/Dockerfile
    witness/stack.yaml
    open-witness/stack.yaml

6. Use latest stack

    stack upgrade
    stack --version

7. Commit and push changes to repo

    git commit -a
    git push

8. Build & test

    VS tasks "Full Build"

9. Upload to Github

    https://github.com/AshleyYakeley/Truth/releases

10. Upload documentation to pinafore.info

    (use script)
    https://pinafore.info/

11. Tag commit

    git tag -a -s VERSION -m "Version VERSION"
    git push --tags

12. Close completed milestone

    https://github.com/AshleyYakeley/Truth/milestones
